qanda.question: Which versions of the Failfast ComfyUI Extensions are currently receiving security updates?
qanda.answer: The 0.x.x version series of the Failfast ComfyUI Extensions is currently supported with security updates.

qanda.question: How can I report a vulnerability in the Failfast ComfyUI Extensions?
qanda.answer: To report a vulnerability, contact the project maintainers through the provided channels. Expect updates on your report and understand the process for accepted or declined vulnerabilities.
